LOOP 3.0 Release Notes
_________
OO MODELS

  [All Models]
- The following module operations were renamed:
    instanceof --> isinstanceof
    subclassof --> issubclassof
    classof    --> getclass
    memberof   --> getmember
    superclass --> getsuper
- Class operation '__init' were renamed to '__new'.
- Classes' metatables contains operations for instropection of inheritance
  hierarchy and other aspects:
    new        (all models)
    rawnew     (all models)
    getmember  (all models)
    members    (all models)
    getsuper   (simple, multiple, multiple2, cached, scoped)
    supers     (simple, multiple, multiple2, cached, scoped)
    allmembers (cached, scoped)
- New module 'loop' provides class introspection operations that work when
  mixing classes from different models.
- New module 'loop.proto' to support dynamic object prototyping.

_____________
CLASS LIBRARY

  [New Classes]
- loop.collection.ArrayedSet (was 'loop.collection.UnorderedArraySet')
- loop.collection.ArrayedMap (was 'loop.collection.MapWithArrayOfKeys')
- loop.collection.CyclicSets
- loop.collection.BiCyclicSets
- loop.collection.SortedMap
- loop.debug.Crawler
- loop.object.Dummy

  [Dropped Classes]
- loop.collection.ObjectCache (see 'loop.table.memoize')
- loop.compiler.Conditional
- loop.compiler.Expression
- loop.debug.Inspector (see module 'inspector')
- loop.thread.Scheduler (see module 'cothread')
- loop.thread.IOScheduler (see module 'cothread')
- loop.thread.SocketScheduler (see module 'cothread' and 'cothread.socket')
- loop.thread.CoSocket (see module 'cothread.socket')
- loop.thread.Timer (see class 'cothread.Timer')

  [loop.collection.OrderedSet]
- New implementation on top of 'loop.collection.CyclicSets'.
- No more field 'firstkey'.

_________________
GENERAL UTILITIES

  [loop.table]
- New method 'memoize'.

_____________
